</code></pre>
If you have writing chops, a strong interest in technology, and a sense for marketing-as-storytelling, we would love to talk to you! Check out our open positions at <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.animalz.co&#x2F;jobs&#x2F;" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.animalz.co&#x2F;jobs&#x2F;</a> -- right now we&#x27;re hiring for Content Marketing Analysts ($50k-$65k depending on experience) and a Head of Content Promotion. And you can email me at jan at animalz.co if you have any specific questions about the positions -- just make sure you actually follow the application protocol on the jobs page too!<p>Thanks!

